{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/e3-project-scorpio-kembali-hadir-dengan-varian-mininya-xbox-one-x/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"E3: Project Scorpio Kembali Hadir Dengan Varian mininya, Xbox One X!","content":"<p>Satu kabar lagi dari E3 (<em>Electronic Entertainment Expo</em>) 2017. Nah, kali ini kita bakal ngebahas khusus tentang XBox. Tahu ga kalau Xbox ternyata akan mengeluarkan produk terbarunya yang dinamai Xbox One X? Belum tau kan? Jadi, Xbox One yang menggunakan label <em>Project Scorpio</em> sudah diakui sebagai varian paling premium. Apalagi jika dilihat dari spesifikasi yang ditawarkan serta harga yang dipatoknya.</p>\n<p>Kira-kira apa aja yang ditawarkan oleh Xbox One X ini? Apakah <em>worth it</em> dengan harganya? Berikut hal-hal yang bisa kamu ketahui mengenai Xbox One X yang diumumkan pada E3 2017 kemarin yang dilansir oleh Gamespot.</p>\n<p>1. Xbox One x merupakan produk Xbox terbaru dengan spesifikasi yang melebihi produk pesaingnya. Dengan mengusung Project Scorpio, Xbox One X berani melabeli produk terbarunya sebagai Console Xbox kelas premium.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_7162\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7162\" data-attachment-id=\"7162\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/e3-project-scorpio-kembali-hadir-dengan-varian-mininya-xbox-one-x/attachment/1-36/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/1-23.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Xbox One X(Sumber: vox-cdn)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Sumber: vox-cdn)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/1-23.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/1-23.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7162\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/1-23.jpg\" alt=\"Xbox One X menclaim dirinya sebagai World's most powerful console (Sumber: vox-cdn)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-7162\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Xbox One X menclaim dirinya sebagai World&#8217;s most powerful console (Sumber: vox-cdn)</p></div>\n<p>2. Xbox One dipatok dengan harga USD 499 dan rencananya akan dirilis pada 7 November mendatang.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_7171\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7171\" data-attachment-id=\"7171\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/e3-project-scorpio-kembali-hadir-dengan-varian-mininya-xbox-one-x/attachment/4-32/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/4-21.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Xbox One X dibandrol dengan harga USD 499 (Sumber: media2.intoday.in)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Xbox One X dibandrol dengan harga USD 499 (Sumber: media2.intoday.in)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/4-21.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/4-21.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7171\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/4-21.jpg\" alt=\"Xbox One X dibandrol dengan harga USD 499 (Sumber: media2.intoday.in)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-7171\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Xbox One X dibandrol dengan harga USD 499 (Sumber: media2.intoday.in)</p></div>\n<p>3. Harga Xbox One lebih murah USD 100 dibandingkan dengan PS4 Pro. Hal ini diyakini akan menimbulkan persaingan pasar yang cukup menarik. Apalagi Xbox One men-<em>claim</em> dirinya lebih kuat dalam hal fitur dan spesifikasi dibandingkan dengan PS4 Pro dengan membawa 8 Core CPU 6 Tera GPU dan 12 GB GDD RAM</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_7177\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7177\" data-attachment-id=\"7177\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/e3-project-scorpio-kembali-hadir-dengan-varian-mininya-xbox-one-x/attachment/6-20/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/6-13.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Sumber: compass.xbox.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Sumber: compass.xbox.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/6-13.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/6-13.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7177\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/6-13.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber: compass.xbox.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-7177\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber: compass.xbox.com)</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_7174\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7174\" data-attachment-id=\"7174\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/e3-project-scorpio-kembali-hadir-dengan-varian-mininya-xbox-one-x/attachment/5-26/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/5-18.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Scorpio Engine (Sumber: compass.xbox.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Scorpio Engine (Sumber: compass.xbox.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/5-18.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/5-18.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7174\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/5-18.jpg\" alt=\"Scorpio Engine (Sumber: compass.xbox.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-7174\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Scorpio Engine (Sumber: compass.xbox.com)</p></div>\n<p>4. Ukuran Xbox One X lebih kecil 40% dibanding ukuran Xbox One sebelumnya. Namun di samping ukurannya yang lebih kecil, <em>console</em> ini memiliki kelebihan karena lebih compact.</p>\n<p>5. Console ini sudah memiliki resolusi 4K UHD</p>\n<p>6. dan HDR, Microsoft menjanjikan 8 juta piksel aktif. Dilihat dari <em>trailer-</em>nya memang menimbulkan banyak sekali ekspektasi karena dalam <em>trailer-</em>nya muncul beberapa <em>game</em> yang memiliki resolusi yang terkenal yahud seperti Metro Exodus, Shadow of War dan Assasins&#8217;s Creed.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_7168\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7168\" data-attachment-id=\"7168\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/e3-project-scorpio-kembali-hadir-dengan-varian-mininya-xbox-one-x/attachment/3-36/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/3-23.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Assasin’s Creed menambah detail dan fitur yang membutuhkan resolusi maksimal (Sumber: vd247.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Assasin’s Creed menambah detail dan fitur yang membutuhkan resolusi maksimal (Sumber: vd247.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/3-23.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/3-23.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7168\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/3-23.jpg\" alt=\"Assasin’s Creed menambah detail dan fitur yang membutuhkan resolusi maksimal (Sumber: vd247.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-7168\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Assasin’s Creed menambah detail dan fitur yang membutuhkan resolusi maksimal (Sumber: vd247.com)</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_7165\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7165\" data-attachment-id=\"7165\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/e3-project-scorpio-kembali-hadir-dengan-varian-mininya-xbox-one-x/attachment/2-33/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/2-20.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Metro Eksodus, memiliki sejarah game dengan resolusi yang besar (Sumber: vox-cdn)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Metro Eksodus, memiliki sejarah game dengan resolusi yang besar (Sumber: vox-cdn)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/2-20.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/2-20.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7165\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/2-20.jpg\" alt=\"Metro Eksodus, memiliki sejarah game dengan resolusi yang besar (Sumber: vox-cdn)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-7165\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Metro Eksodus, memiliki sejarah game dengan resolusi yang besar (Sumber: vox-cdn)</p></div>\n<p>Berikut <em>trailer-</em>nya,</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/g-gp-Voq6MQ\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Selain itu, Xbox One X juga merilis beberapa <em>game</em> yang bisa dimainkan di Xbox One X, antara lain Osiri 3, Paladins, Raider Battleground, Uruly Playfround, Frontline, Battlerite, Surviving Mars dll. Untuk mengerti lebih dalam mengenai <em>game console</em> terbaru, XBox One X, mari kita simak <em>review-</em>nya bersama IGN.</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/8p_FmpWFwmU\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"98cad228-f026-56e1-b921-bc73519de223"}}}